n \rightarrow\infty
S_n= \frac{{1}}{{n}}\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-\bar{X_n})^2
=\frac{{1}}{{n}}[\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-u)^2+2(X_i-u)(u-\bar{X_n})+(u-\bar{X_n})^2)]
=\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-u)^2+\frac{2}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-u)(u-\bar{X_n})+(u-\bar{X_n})^2
=\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-u)^2+2(u-\bar{X_n})\frac{{1}}{{n}}\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-u)+(u-\bar{X_n})^2
=\frac{{1}}{{n}}\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-u)^2+2(u-\bar{X_n})\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i)-u+(u-\bar{X_n})^2
=\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-u)^2+2(u-\bar{X_n})(\bar{X_n}-u)+(u-\bar{X_n})^2
=\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-u)^2-(\bar{X_n}-u)^2
\bar{X} =\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i) \rightarrow u\text{ almost surely}
\frac{1}{n}\sum_{i=1}^n(X_i-\bar{X_n})^2 \rightarrow u E((X_i-\bar{X_n})^2) = Var(X) \text{ almost surely}
